X:1114031
T:Canadian Reel
S:Old Grey Goose, $2Old Time Country Song & Dance Band.$0 Cassette (self-produced),
S:recorded in Liberty and Montvile, ME, 1993. They learned it from Gale Huntington
S:of Martha's Vineyard.
H:This is a tune I remember hearing from Bowdoinham dances with the Maine
H:Country Dance Orchestra long ago. They often played it with the Dominion
H:Reel. There's another transcription from a recording Doug Protsik made
H:for the Maine Fiddle Camp website <https://www.mainefiddlecamp.org> in 2020.
N:From NH Country Dance (URL below), along with many New England, Canadian & Swedish
N:tunes, and resources for abc notation and New England traditional music and dance.
