X:3128070
T:Hot Punch
S:Doug Protsik, recording made at Maine Fiddle Camp, 1998.
S:Maine Country Dance Orchestra, Bowdoinham Contradance, played many times, 1980s.
H:This was a tune played fairly frequently at the Bowdoinham dance. It's a
H:Scottish tune, possibly originally a pipe tune. This transcription is based on
H:a recording of Doug Protsik playing the tune for me on a piano.
