S:Normand Miron, recorded at a QuÃ©becois Social Dance session at Northern
S:Week at Ashokan, 1998. Chords are transcribed as accurately as possible.
H:Normand is a well known QuÃ©bÃ©cois button accordion player. Jean Marie 
H:Verret was also playing which may have affected Normand's melody at times. 
H:Normand is very expressive, but much of it isn't easily written down; it 
H:involves subtle use of the bellows and subtle timing that isn't easy to 
H:notate. I included a few idiosyncratic melodic and timing details that 
H:he didn't play every time to give more of a sense of his playing style.
