X:5029500
T:Mungal\aaten
S:Eric och Kalle Sahlstr\"om, $2Vi e ju Uplenningar ve,$0 Valbo 1974. Jougo
S:Music, JGOCD02, CD, 2004.
H:Transcribed from the playing of Eric and Kalle Sahlstr\"om. To the extent
H:the tune is accompanied it's through harmony, so I don't include chords.
H:This is a tune from Munga in Uppland. According to the Swedish Wikipedia
H:it was played by C. G. Englund, a nyckelharpa player from Munga at a fiddling
H:competition in 1910, and immediately became very popular. The recording
H:this is transcribed from is a concert recording, and the audience starts
H:singing in the background part way through.
