X:2802501
T:Gr\/onl\aenderpolka
T:Polka from Greenland
S:Olivia und Lars beim Kulturnatten 2013 in NUUK, https://youtu.be/nkxMGGH71Ss,
S:March 4, 2013.
H:Translation: Olivia and Lars at the Kulturnatten 2013 in NUUK.
H:Played in D, then switched to A; transcribed separately in each key.
H:I haven't been able to find any more about the musicians although they're very good.
H:I have also transcribed a version by Thomas M\/oller, harmonica and Anders J. \/Orts
H:(guitar) in C. Each is somewhat different, with its own interesting variations.
H:I include an arrangement I put together that tries to keep the spirit of the
H:tune while combining many of the most enjoyable variations.
H:It's really a Greenland polka; I keep it with Scandinavian tunes for convenience.
