X:6764520
T:Road to Boston Polska
C:Peter Yarensky, 12-9-20
H:This is a variation on Road to Boston that has been hinted at here and there
H:for years. I've attempted it in the past with some success, but this version
H:which came to me in the shower is the first I've heard or come up with that is
H:clearly Road to Boston as a hambo and that also sounds at least vaguely Swedish.
