X:6999540
T:Selmer Ramsey's Old Time Schottische No. 3
S:$2Selmer Ramsey's Old Time Music Volume 1.$0 Mark Custom Records, MC6197, 1977.
H:Selmer Ramsey (1914-1978) was a Minnesota fiddler. He played for dances around 
H:the state for many years, and composed several tunes. This is from the first 
H:of his three records.
