X:2430590
%%pagescale .9
T:Frankie's Kolomejka
C:Frankie Rodgers
S:Frankie Rodgers & Gaby Haas, $2Play for a Horilka Party.$0 Point Records, PS 302, 1968.
H:As played by  Frankie Rodgers.
H:So how did Frankie Rodgers come to write a kolomejka? In 2002 Albert Brien had a
H:concert/workshop in the Fiddler's Loft in Kingston, NH with British Colombia fiddler
H:Yvonne Hernandez. She played the tune and taught it during the workshop. I asked her
H:that question. Her mother, who was in the audience called out that despite his name,
H:Frankie was of Ukrainian background.
